  <reg:acttitle>Geothermal Resources Act</reg:acttitle>
  <reg:title>Geothermal Geophysical Exploration Regulation</reg:title>
  <reg:amsincluded>[includes amendments up to B.C. Reg. 39/2017, March 31, 2017]</reg:amsincluded>
  <reg:regpitid>358_98_pit</reg:regpitid>
  <reg:content>
    <bcl:section id="d2e33" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Repealed</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>Repealed. [B.C. Reg. 39/2017, Sch. 1, s. 1.]</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e51">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Application of regulations under the <in:doc>Oil and Gas Activities Act</in:doc></bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e61">
        <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The Geophysical Exploration Regulation, other than section 12, under the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/08036_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Oil and Gas Activities Act</in:doc></bcl:link> applies for the purposes of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96171_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Geothermal Resources Act</in:doc></bcl:link> to exploration for geothermal resources.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d2e76">
        <bcl:num>2</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>Repealed. [B.C. Reg. 39/2017, Sch. 1, s. 2.]</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:subsection id="d3e76">
        <bcl:num>3</bcl:num>
        <bcl:text>The Geophysical Exploration Regulation, as it applies for the purposes of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96171_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Geothermal Resources Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, must be read as if references to the Act are references to the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96171_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Geothermal Resources Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, and references to a geophysical permit holder are read as references to a person carrying out exploration for geothermal resources.</bcl:text>
      </bcl:subsection>
      <bcl:hnote>[am. B.C. Reg. 39/2017, Sch. 1, s. 2.]</bcl:hnote>
    </bcl:section>
    <reg:provisionsnote>[Provisions relevant to the enactment of this regulation: <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/96171_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Geothermal Resources Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, R.S.B.C. 1996, c. 171, section 24 (2) (c)]</reg:provisionsnote>
  </reg:content>
